{"tid":1951302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗同五毛又用翻雨傘後期個招叫人去做狗 大家小心","createTime":"2020-03-31T01:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T05:30:25.000Z","uid":288670,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e5c3cf75b8950f31855984679403d49993809d","tid":1951302,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"大家小心 五毛網軍開始用翻雨傘後期個招叫人去做狗<br />\n<br />\n多左人做狗 狗就會話大部份年輕人都支持狗支持港共 只有少部份人被洗腦<br />\n<br />\n我地又會變翻少數派 今日已經有另一隻五毛開post 叫人去做狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0v5FC2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0v5FC2R.png&h=49da69df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲入 男朋友打算大招去考警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1950602\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1950602</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另一個五毛網軍post <br />\n<br />\n大家係咪寧願成個警隊 一個白警都無？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同埋有大量五毛/狗隻附和推post 連登仔小心"},{"pid":"932c7630282c1a94669bd79f5396aba9c3a91214","tid":1951302,"uid":195248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日係831七個月  大量五毛開黑警想淡化po</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"14ac8feb19406d6e901bff76033e600f6a40b361","tid":1951302,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到post 其他人唔該長期幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n咪撚俾五毛同狗得逞"},{"pid":"8cc16c1f3feb9adc94f2474a56375ed94d5f739c","tid":1951302,"uid":195248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:58:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日係831七個月  大量五毛開黑警po想淡化今晚行動</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cd1c127c9cafb1bc0164e3f1e3b911675b20c569","tid":1951302,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0207ab5d6b9072046be6fe3deec30bd3ebf66b9","tid":1951302,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"903140a59c3276f95d23ce22b571873a013f9f56","tid":1951302,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"狗又名黨衛軍<br />\n<br />\n不如直接話加入共產黨做臥底，一步步做上國家主席<br />\n<br />\n白咩撚野狗"},{"pid":"5ce99e603905736e8e99876fc4e249df3b3f7f17","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f51e506d4eb54a9b3a3b18a5bb4af3e7f5aac8a9","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"你估呢個世界咁多人做到李登輝？"},{"pid":"c097b13f2d0216fdb9c6fd16dc7e9af0b050c49c","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f51e506d4eb54a9b3a3b18a5bb4af3e7f5aac8a9","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"你估呢個世界咁多人做到李登輝？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"仲要係一班書都讀唔成嘅人？"},{"pid":"34324a0262ae89ff5916bb3f5d430dbafc673978","tid":1951302,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ac8feb19406d6e901bff76033e600f6a40b361","tid":1951302,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到post 其他人唔該長期幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n咪撚俾五毛同狗得逞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abbfe6f0f41f9fb53977bba71e4f1a3486161aa8","tid":1951302,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c097b13f2d0216fdb9c6fd16dc7e9af0b050c49c","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f51e506d4eb54a9b3a3b18a5bb4af3e7f5aac8a9","tid":1951302,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"你估呢個世界咁多人做到李登輝？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:11:13.000Z","msg